name: Black Garden Ribbon Necklace
description:
Totally Tres Chic!

A sophisticated take on the floral bib! An elegant mix of black, clear and brown/gold glass beads, it has a sculputral feel of a real work of art around your neck.

The black satin ribbon makes the necklace adjustable - wear it as a choker or lower down your chest!

Comes in a tulle pouch.

Accent piece: 7 x 3.75 inches
Necklace length: 34.5 inches

name: Copper Wire Floral Necklace
description:
Copper wires keeps this piece current with a mix of various beads and copper wire balls.

Wear this with shirts and tanks or use this necklace to up the ante of your little black dress!

Comes in a tulle pouch.

Flower details: around 3 x 2 inches each
Necklace length (from hook to ring): 21 inches
Necklace drop: 7.75 inches

name: Wire and Glass Bar Necklace - Black and Fuschia
description:
Be a stand out with this exotic piece!

This Egyptian inspired choker is made of a satin blend circlet in black anchored by a large bar made of wire and accented by 4 large glass beads.

I love pairing this particularly with strapless dresses or tube tops and tanks with jeans!

Comes in a tulle pouch.

Bar: 7 x 1.75 inches
Necklace length (from hook to ring): 17 inches
Circlet extender chain: 1.5 inches
Circlet drop from clasp to bottom (without pendant): 4.75 inches

* As this bib is made of wire, it is normal for it not to lay perfectly flat against the neck/chest area. The bar itself is bendable to suit one's needs, curving it tighter around the neck or flat against the collar bone.
